title: [PS3] Rogero CFW 4.50 v1.01
description: PlayStation 3 CFW Developer Rogero is back following his recent Custom Firmware (CFW) Release for version 4.50 firmware. Recently, the developer released version 1.01 and the developer has made sure extensive testing on various models was done to this release. This update packs alot of changes from the PlayStation 3 Developer (Rogero). Added was the ToolBox to restore multiMAN/StealthMAN for 4.50. The XMB In-Game Screenshot was added to Rogero's 1.01 update, Then also Cinavia has been patched on the HDD only and some other changes you view in the developers changelog with additional information about this CFW release.
